{"word":"Abomination","slug":"abomination","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Abomination</b> Things that are, to God:<br/> - Idolatry<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=7&verse=25'>Deu 7:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=27&verse=15'>Deu 27:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=32&verse=16'>Deu 32:16</a> <br/> - Unjust weights and measures<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=25&verse=16'>Deu 25:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=11&verse=1'>Pro 11:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=20&verse=10'>Pro 20:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=20&verse=23'>Pro 20:23</a> <br/> - Uncleanness<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=18&verse=22'>Lev 18:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=20&verse=13'>Lev 20:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=24&verse=4'>Deu 24:4</a> <br/> - Incest<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=18&verse=18'>Lev 18:18</a> <br/> - Lying with a woman in her menses<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=18&verse=19'>Lev 18:19</a> <br/> - Adultery<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=18&verse=20'>Lev 18:20</a> <br/> - Sodomy<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=18&verse=23'>Lev 18:23</a> <br/> - Offering seed to Molech<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=18&verse=21'>Lev 18:21</a> <br/> - Offering children in sacrifice<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=18&verse=10'>Deu 18:10</a> <br/> - Sorcery and Necromancy<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=18&verse=11'>Deu 18:11</a> <br/> - The hire of a whore and price of a dog, as a consecrated gift<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/